fields.Description: Application for naturalisation as a British citizen Important: Before completing this form, you should read the Guide AN as well as theBooklet AN. Fill in those parts of the form that apply to your application. If there is notenough space for your answer, use age 22 to provide additional information.If you want help to complete your application form, you may wish to contact acompetent adviser, for example a solicitor or agent registered with the Office of theImmigration Services Commissioner (see page 6 of the Guide AN which ccompaniesthis form for details). Or you may wish to use the Nationality Checking Service operatedby a number of local authorities. Your Register Office will advise if one is operated inyour area.
